<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Reminder for the upcoming event: <%= @event.name %></h2>
    <p>
			This is a friendly reminder that the date for the event is <%= @event.display_start_time %>. </p>

		<p> If you need to update your rsvp response (e.g. Number of additional guest you are bringing, your rsvp comment and/or what you are bringing to the party), please login to <%= link_to 'Lets Gather', root_url %> and do so ASAP to inform the host of any changes from your end.  You may also contact your host at <%= @event.user.email %> for any further inquiries.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>

